<db:para>This example is an implementation of a simple jigsaw puzzle game using Qt's drag and drop API. The <db:link xlink:href="qtwidgets-itemviews-puzzle-example.xml">Item View Puzzle</db:link> example shows many of the same features, but takes an alternative approach that uses Qt's model/view framework to manage drag and drop operations.</db:para>
